---
source: crates/tirith/tests/help_snapshots.rs
expression: stdout.to_string()
---
Manage file checkpoints for rollback (experimental)

Usage: tirith checkpoint <COMMAND>

Commands:
  create   Create a checkpoint of specified paths
  list     List all checkpoints
  restore  Restore files from a checkpoint
  diff     Show differences between checkpoint and current state
  purge    Remove old checkpoints based on age/count/size limits
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help

Examples:
  tirith checkpoint create src/ Cargo.toml
  tirith checkpoint list
  tirith checkpoint restore <id>
  tirith checkpoint diff <id>
  tirith checkpoint purge
